  3.965425659530676*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eb6fa357-27b2-814c-bd4b-\
1bb24fef4467"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Optional: Define multiplets before running ",
 Cell[BoxData[
 "generateSRs"], "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->
  "0cff002e-ce3c-e54d-b6fd-e6eb172c6ca5"],
 ". Alternatively, you can directly input multiplets into the function.\n\n\
Particles must be ordered from HIGHEST to LOWEST m within multiplets. \
Particle multiplets must be a list of strings corresponding to the names of \
the particles. The Hamiltonian list may contain symbolic variables to \
represent CKM factors."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9669591818431606`*^9, 3.96695918508737*^9}, {
  3.966959215130106*^9, 3.966959249026575*^9}, {3.970784561795349*^9, 
